{"id": "1396879109195436235", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 0, "author_id": "667108912033431575", "author_name": "gripito", "author_bot": false, "content": "vc usaria na nautila pq, se vc está usando ela?", "timestamp": "2025-07-21T15:38:52.391000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1396879598003818507", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 0, "author_id": "667108912033431575", "author_name": "gripito", "author_bot": false, "content": "já recomendo nunca usar o reset em unit limitada ou especial, sempre nas comuns.  Caecus, Goliath, é bom manter pq usa bastante. Eu não uso Alva nem Sanga, e se vc n está usando nas suas comps, então melhor resetar esses", "timestamp": "2025-07-21T15:40:48.932000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1396879960345542696", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 0, "author_id": "667108912033431575", "author_name": "gripito", "author_bot": false, "content": "mas n entendi pq vc n está usando Hameln, q é um support moh bom, no teu time. Vc pode usar Gdoll+Myrian para poison+exalt, e Hameln para dar efeito dobrado nas cartas OU diminuir 2 custos. Vc tem murphy e tulu tbm, pode juntar os 2 + Myrian e fazer um time q da tentaculada o tempo todo", "timestamp": "2025-07-21T15:42:15.321000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1396880099546103899", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 0, "author_id": "667108912033431575", "author_name": "gripito", "author_bot": false, "content": "Nautila é boa, mas ela é boa gerando escudo, n acho q ela traga algo tão relevante para comp (exceto se tiver mto alto o dano). A ramona alternativa ai n tenho, então n posso opinar", "timestamp": "2025-07-21T15:42:48.509000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1396881602952560700", "channel_id": "1300659718653476925", "type": 19, "author_id": "190519309393461248", "author_name": "vensas", "author_bot": false, "content": "Era mais por que eu uso ela pelo fato de ter muitas cópias delas", "timestamp": "2025-07-21T15:48:46.949000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["667108912033431575"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1396879109195436235", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
